#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:17
#, no-c-format
msgid "<command>bzip2</command> is a compression program."
msgstr "<command>bzip2</command> je kompresijski program."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:19
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The bzip2 KIO worker is not directly usable, and is intended for use as a "
"filter. For example, the tar KIO worker can filter a file through the bzip2 "
"KIO worker, in order to display the contents of a <literal role=\"extension"
"\">tar.bz2</literal> file directly in a &konqueror; window."
msgstr ""
"Bzip2 KIO worker ni neposredno uporaben, in je namenjen, da se ga uporablja "
"kot filter, npr. tar KIO worker lahko filtrira datoteko s pomočjo bzip2 KIO "
"worker-ja, da bi lahko neposredno prikazal vsebino datoteke <literal role="
"\"extension\">tar.bz2</literal> v oknu &konqueror;."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:25
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you click on a file compressed with a <literal role=\"extension\">.bz2</"
"literal> in &konqueror;, this KIO worker is used to uncompress it and "
"display it as a normal (uncompressed) file."
msgstr ""
"Če v &konqueror;-ju kliknete na datoteko stisnjeno z <literal role="
"\"extension\">.bz2</literal>, se ta KIO worker uporabi za razširjenje "
"datoteke in jo prikaže kot običajno, nestisnjeno datoteko."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:29
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you are a developer, and would like to use the bzip2 filter, you can find "
"documentation on using KIO workers at <ulink url=\"http://techbase.kde.org"
"\">http://techbase.kde.org</ulink>"
msgstr ""
"Če ste razvijalec in bi želeli uporabiti bzip2 filter, lahko najdete "
"dokumentacijo o uporabi KIO worker-jev na <ulink url=\"http://developer.kde."
"org\">http://developer.kde.org</ulink>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:33
#, no-c-format
msgid "See the manual: <ulink url=\"man:/bzip2\">bzip2</ulink>."
msgstr "Oglejte si priročnik: <ulink url=\"man:/bzip2\">bzip2</ulink>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:36
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<command>bzip</command> is the ancestor of bzip2. It is rarely used today, "
"having been replaced with bzip2, which offers much better compression."
msgstr ""
"<command>bzip</command> je predhodnik bzip2-a. Danes je redkeje uporabljen, "
"saj ga je nadomestil bzip2, ki ponuja veliko boljšo kompresijo."

#~ msgid "bzip2"
#~ msgstr "bzip2"
